Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管說多少次都休想我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請投降 請投降 請立刻投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 請投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是死 我也不會投降…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 快溜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話聽到過很多次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是表達感謝的慣用句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 他幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位少年您打算如何處理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…如果換成西布隆 他會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也會請你大吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝…
